The paper is about scene text recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves semantic segmentation and RNN, which are also commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions aligning with target characters, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR).
